    "Akiba et al. (2025) optimize merging strategies via evolutionary search.",
    "Post-training or model linearization can further improve mergeability (Yang et al., 2024b; Ortiz-Jimenez et al., 2023; Tang et al., 2024b; Liu et al., 2024).",
    "Subspace Merging Methods.",
    "Recent approaches treat merging as a problem within low-rank task subspaces rather than full parameter space.",
    "Skorobogat et al. (2025) address the rank collapse of task vectors with subspace-boosted merging, using SVD to preserve expressive directions."
